  "itemdesc-herbball-archer": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>苦涩干硬，吃完后眼睛有些发酸。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-healingeffect": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>油腻发苦，像过期的药膏。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-hungerenhance": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>通畅。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-hungersupress": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>又干又硬，不过挺有嚼头。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-hunter": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>腥咸粗糙，像嚼了一口没风干好的肉。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-looter": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>似乎只对搜索瓶瓶罐罐有效……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-melee": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>像干嚼了维生素C和B！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-mining": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>有沙粒感，嚼起来甚至有点硌牙。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-poison": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>嗯！很甜！等等，我吃了多少？！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-predator": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>动物比往常更喜欢你……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-regen": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>一块巧克力。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-scentmask": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>这有味道吗？</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-speed": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>把它当成咸味零食似乎不错……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-herbball-vitality": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>吃完胸口发闷。</i></font><br>",

