  "itemdesc-potionportion-archer-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>苦涩干硬，吃完后眼睛有些发酸。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-archer-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>瞄准时，连风都摒住了呼吸。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-archer-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>跳蚤看起来像车轮那么大！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-healingeffect-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>油腻发苦，像过期的药膏。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-healingeffect-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>尝起来很浓郁，有奶油的味道。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-healingeffect-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>喝咖啡时多放点吧！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hungerenhance-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>通畅。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hungerenhance-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>通畅！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hungerenhance-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>通畅！！！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hungersupress-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>又干又硬，不过挺有嚼头。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hungersupress-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>散发着芒果的芬芳。喝了这个我可以跑整整一天！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hungersupress-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>嗝~</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hunter-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>腥咸粗糙，像嚼了一口没风干好的肉。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hunter-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>这里没有素食主义者。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-hunter-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>你的冰箱还放得下吗？</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-looter-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>似乎只对搜索瓶瓶罐罐有效……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-looter-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>似乎只对搜索瓶瓶罐罐有效……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-looter-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>似乎只对搜索瓶瓶罐罐有效……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-melee-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>像干嚼了维生素C和B！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-melee-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>好像熟悉的运动饮料，菠萝味！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-melee-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>我想喝菠萝啤了。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-mining-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>有沙粒感，嚼起来甚至有点硌牙。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-mining-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>石头看起来比往常更好欺负。有荔枝的味道。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-mining-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>效率V，时运III。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-poison-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>嗯！很甜！等等，我吃了多少？！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-poison-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>小心！不过话说回来闻起来像草莓……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-poison-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>无色无味，这才是毒药该有的样子！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-predator-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>动物比往常更喜欢你……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-predator-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>动物比往常更喜欢你……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-predator-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>动物比往常更喜欢你……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-regen-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>一块巧克力。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-regen-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>热可可味，多加点巧克力？</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-regen-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>其实你30秒只需要喝一罐的……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-scentmask-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>这有味道吗？</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-scentmask-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>你闻起来像一块石头。不过这喝起来是石榴味的。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-scentmask-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>无异味！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-speed-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>把它当成咸味零食似乎不错……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-speed-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>有点电解质的咸味。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-speed-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>太好了，喝了这个我不会眩晕！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-vitality-weak": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>吃完胸口发闷。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-vitality-medium": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>好像看到一个金色的大只佬……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-potionportion-vitality-strong": "<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>你感觉你像是两心三肺的炽天使……嗯？蚁牛是什么？？！</i></font><br>",

  "itemdesc-utilitypotionportion-recall": "使用药水时：你将传送回上次的归位点。\n\n<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>蓝莓口味！多喝点！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-utilitypotionportion-glow": "使用药水时：你将散发出明亮的光芒。\n\n<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>家常柠檬水，但是似乎不太对劲……</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-utilitypotionportion-waterbreathe": "使用药水时：你可以在水下呼吸。\n\n<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>尝起来像海鲜汤，最好趁热喝。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-utilitypotionportion-temporal": "使用药水时：你将获得一些时间稳定值。\n\n<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>口感冰冰凉，碎裂的时空齿轮就像薄荷冰沙！</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-utilitypotionportion-nutrition": "使用药水时：你将在较低的营养项上回复饱食度，但会损失较高营养项的饱食度。\n\n<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>尝起来像你最不喜欢吃的食物，不过我敢肯定这对你有好处。</i></font><br>",
  "itemdesc-utilitypotionportion-reshape": "使用药水时：你可以使用 .charsel 命令重塑你的外貌与角色起源。\n\n<font color=\"#99c9f9\"><i>红色药丸还是蓝色药丸，这次仔细选！</i></font><br>",

